WF-002 | Open Bulk Import page | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Import Client | on_success: opens Bulk Import page
WF-003 | Search clients | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Client_Search | on_success: filters client list by search query (Name, Account No., External ID, or Mobile Number)
WF-004 | Filter clients by Status | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Status_Filter | on_success: filters client list by selected status
WF-005 | Open Client Detail from listing | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Open Client Detail | on_success: navigates to Client Detail page for selected client
